<D>__{kramer...}
<A>__{she breaks off, uncertain whether or not to go on. then, making up her mind, she reaches across, takes ted's scotch and soda and drinks half of it down in one gulp.}
<C>__{phyllis}
<P>__{(in a rush)}
<D>__{o'connor's out to get you. he's going to take the fire and ice account away from you.}
