<P>__{(stunned)}
<D>__{what?!?}
<A>__{phyllis nods.}
<C>__{ted}
<P>__{(angry)}
<D>__{i don't believe it! that's crazy! why would jim do something like that?}
<A>__{phyllis polishes off the rest of ted's drink.}
<C>__{phyllis}
<P>__{(angry herself)}
<D>__{you want to know why? i will tell you why...}
